get_wastewater_latest¶

outbreak_data.get_wastewater_latest(**kwargs)¶

Get date of latest wastewater sample matching a given query. Same parameters as get_wastewater_samples.

Returns

The date of the most recent matching sample in YYYY-MM-DD.

Parameter example

{ ‘region’: ‘Ohio’, ‘server’: ‘dev.outbreak.info’ }
